text: National Highway 128A, commonly referred to as NH 128A is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 28. NH-128A runs in the state of Uttar Pradesh in India. == Route == NH128A connects Mohammadpur, Badshapur and Jaunpur in the state of Uttar Pradesh. == Junctions == : Terminal near Mohammadpur. : Terminal near Jaunpur. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 128A on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Uttar Pradesh
